          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9" data-video-steps-target="step" data-step="2" data-start-time="6" data-end-time="12">
            <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900/40 data-[active]:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
              <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 size-5 text-blue-600/40 data-[active]:text-blue-600 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M15.312 11.424a5.5 5.5 0 0 1-9.201 2.466l-.312-.311h2.433a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5H3.989a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v4.242a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0v-2.43l.31.31a7 7 0 0 0 11.712-3.138.75.75 0 0 0-1.449-.39Zm1.23-3.723a.75.75 0 0 0 .219-.53V2.929a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0V5.36l-.31-.31A7 7 0 0 0 3.239 8.188a.75.75 0 1 0 1.448.389A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 13.89 6.11l.311.31h-2.432a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h4.243a.75.75 0 0 0 .53-.219Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Generate.
            </dt>
            <dd class="inline text-gray-600/40 data-[active]:text-gray-600 transition-colors">AI transforms your reusable template into a personalized reply.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9" data-video-steps-target="step" data-step="3" data-start-time="12" data-end-time="20">
            <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900/40 data-[active]:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
              <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 size-5 text-blue-600/40 data-[active]:text-blue-600 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                <path d="M3.105 2.288a.75.75 0 0 0-.826.95l1.414 4.926A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 5.135 9.25h6.115a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H5.135a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.442 1.086l-1.414 4.926a.75.75 0 0 0 .826.95 28.897 28.897 0 0 0 15.293-7.155.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.114A28.897 28.897 0 0 0 3.105 2.288Z" />
              </svg>
              Send.
            </dt>
            <dd class="inline text-gray-600/40 data-[active]:text-gray-600 transition-colors">Review every reply before it sends. You always have the final say.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <video
          data-video-steps-target="video"
          class="w-full rounded-lg border border-stone-200 shadow-lg"
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="">
          <source src="https://assets.vipreply.ai/three-click-reply-optimized.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
